Unbound Snake v0.1
Carlos Alberto Ramos Lopez, December 2011
email: UnboundDarkness@gmail.com

Description
----------------------------------------------------
Unbound Snake is a game written in Python/PyGame licensed under GPL.

To run it, enter the source code directory and execute:
python UnboundSnake.py

Controls:
	Left    - Left Arrow
	Right   - Right Arrow
	Up      - Up Arrow
	Down    - Down Arrow
	Exit    - Escape
	Restart - F5 (When Game Over)
